<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB07976</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT PROVIDING FOR THE CONSTRUCTION OF PUBLIC RESTROOMS ALONG NATIONAL AND PROVINCIAL HIGHWAYS THROUGHOUT THE COUNTRY, APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT :  Provides for the construction of public restrooms every 30 to 50 kilometers apart along national and provincial roads nationwide.  Allows the Sanggunian/NGO of the particular barangay where it is situated to collect reasonable usage fee which shall be used for the development projects of the corresponding barangay. </td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ALIAS NAME : “Land Transport Support Facilities for Hygiene and Convenience Act.”</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>NIETO, JOHN MARVIN &quot;YUL SERVO&quot; C., MACEDA, EDWARD VERA PEREZ, MARTINEZ, ERIC M., SANDOVAL, FEDERICO &quot;RICKY&quot; II S., MALAPITAN, DALE &quot;ALONG&quot; R., OLIVAREZ, ERIC L., SALO, RON P., MONTORO, TEODORO &quot;TED&quot; G., CALIXTO-RUBIANO, EMI G.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-07-30</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Del Mar (000 2018-08-08)</td><td>2. Tambunting (000 2018-08-15)</td><tr><td>3. Sy-Alvarado (000 2018-08-16)</td><td>4. Silverio (000 2018-08-22)</td><tr><td>5. Bravo (M.) (000 2018-11-21)</td><td>6. Hernandez (P.) (000 2018-12-18)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON PUBLIC WORKS AND HIGHWAYS ON 2018-08-06</td></tr></table>